  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/14/apple-reportedly-hiring-new-talent-to-solve-iwatch-design-proble/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/untitled-1-1360615169.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n目前已有不同的传闻、<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/05/28/tim-cook-thinks-google-glass-lacks-broad-appeal-but-wearables-a/\">消息</a>以及<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/01/apple-files-application-to-register-iwatch-trademark-in-japan/\">专利</a>去<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/02/21/apple-patent-application-flexible-display-band/\">单方面证明</a> Apple <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/iWatch/\">iWatch</a> 有可能正在开发中，而据 Financial Times 的线报指出，Apple 在过去几个星期里为这款传说中的产品「积极地」招揽人手开发。线人表示 Apple 已经脱离了 iWatch 的<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/02/10/nyt-apple-experimenting-with-wrist-worn-ios-devices-using-curved-glass/\">探索期</a>，进入了真正开发的阶段，其开发团队亦已有几十人了，只是基于「一些他们未能解决的艰难工程问题」而需要增聘人手。不过既然现在仍然在礼聘的话，那估计这款产品在短期内都不会被发布了，不想等的话，可以先自行拿 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2011/01/01/hex-ships-ipod-nano-watch-band-dares-you-to-destroy-it-video/\">iPod nano 加表带</a>解解渴吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/07/14/apple-reportedly-hiring-new-talent-to-solve-iwatch-design-proble/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/0/0a3cbfce-ec0f-11e2-bfdb-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2Z3zJClij\">Financial</a></div>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/14/apple-reportedly-hiring-new-talent-to-solve-iwatch-design-proble/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20665486/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章